link:labelLink.link:label: Superannuation
Superannuation Contribution Pooled Super Trusts Contributions Amount

This is the value, during the relevant period, for superannuation entities that are pooled super trusts. Record the dollar value of contributions income received and receivable from pooled super trust members for the period to date, including contributions from self-employed members.
Do not include 'rollovers received'. Show contributions gross of contributions tax and do not deduct entry fees, deferred entry fees, commissions, management fees or any other ongoing fees or charges deducted from the contributions received (where applicable to the superannuation entity).
Superannuation Payment Benefit Lump Sum Compassionate Grounds Amount
This is the value, during the relevant period, for the expense for benefits paid to members by the trustee(s) under the early release provisions relating to compassionate grounds.
Superannuation Payment Benefit Lump Sum Death Amount

This is the value, during the relevant period, for the expense for benefits that have been paid by the trustee to the nominated beneficiary/dependent or the deceased member's estate due to the death of a member.
Superannuation Payment Benefit Lump Sum Disability Amount
This is the value, during the relevant period, for the expense for benefits paid to members resulting from total and permanent disability, and for temporary disability/income protection.
Superannuation Payment Benefit Lump Sum Financial Hardship Amount
This is the value, during the relevant period, for the expense for benefits paid to members by the trustee(s) under the early release provisions relating to grounds of severe financial hardship.
Superannuation Payment Benefit Lump Sum Financial Hardship And Compassionate Grounds Amount

This is the value, during the relevant period, for the expense for benefits paid to members by the trustee(s) under the early release provisions relating to severe financial hardship or compassionate grounds.
Superannuation Payment Benefit Lump Sum Resignation Amount
This is the value, during the relevant period, for the expense for benefits paid to members as a result of member resignation from the employer.
Superannuation Payment Benefit Lump Sum Retirement Amount

This is the value, during the relevant period, for the expense for benefits paid to members as a result of retirement. This does not include amounts paid to members' accounts with other superannuation entities.
Superannuation Payment Benefit Lump Sum Retrenchment And Redundancies Amount
This is the value, during the relevant period, for the expense for benefits paid to members as a result of retrenchment or redundancy.
Superannuation Payment Benefit Pensions Amount

This is the value, during the relevant period, for the total value of benefits paid to members in the form of a pension. Includes complying pension, allocated pension and annuity payments. Do not include amounts resulting from the commutation of pension benefits.
Superannuation Payment Benefit Total Amount
This is the value, during the relevant period, for the total of all lump sum and pension benefit paid directly to members, i.e. excluding rollovers.
Superannuation Payment Lump Sum Pooled Super Trusts Amount
This is the value, during the relevant period, for superannuation entities that are pooled super trusts. Report the expense for payments to unit holders.
